nestopia
------------------------------------------
This project is a fork of the original Nestopia source code, plus the Linux
port. The purpose of the project is to enhance the original, and ensure it
continues to work on modern operating systems.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.2.0-1
  libGL1-19.1.6-1
  libSDL2_2.0_0-2.0.7-1
  libarchive13-3.5.2-1
  libfltk1.3-1.3.4-1
  libgcc1-11.2.0-1
  libstdc++6-11.2.0-1
  zlib0-1.2.11-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  autoconf-13-1
  automake-11-1
  binutils-2.37-1
  cygport-0.34.0-1
  gcc-core-11.2.0-1
  gcc-g++-11.2.0-1
  libGL-devel-19.1.6-1
  libSDL2-devel-2.0.7-1
  libarchive-devel-3.5.2-1
  libfltk-devel-1.3.4-1
  make-4.3-1
  zlib-devel-1.2.11-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/0ldsk00l/nestopia

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/0ldsk00l/nestopia/archive/refs/tags/1.51.1.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack nestopia-1.51.1-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./nestopia-1.51.1-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/nestopia-1.51.1-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/nestopia-1.51.1-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(nestopia)
  /etc/postinstall/nestopia.sh
  /usr/bin/nestopia.exe
  /usr/share/applications/nestopia.desktop
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/nestopia.README
  /usr/share/doc/nestopia/COPYING
  /usr/share/doc/nestopia/ChangeLog
  /usr/share/doc/nestopia/Copyright
  /usr/share/doc/nestopia/README.md
  /usr/share/doc/nestopia/html/readme.html
  /usr/share/icons/hicolor/128x128/apps/nestopia.png
  /usr/share/icons/hicolor/32x32/apps/nestopia.png
  /usr/share/icons/hicolor/48x48/apps/nestopia.png
  /usr/share/icons/hicolor/64x64/apps/nestopia.png
  /usr/share/icons/hicolor/96x96/apps/nestopia.png
  /usr/share/icons/hicolor/scalable/apps/nespad.svg
  /usr/share/icons/hicolor/scalable/apps/nestopia.svg
  /usr/share/nestopia/NstDatabase.xml

